<item>
            <title>[LU-18524] Improve lctl nodemap_modify user interface</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18524</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be beneficial to slightly improve the &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lctl nodemap_modify&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; interface for easier use, consolidating the&#160; &lt;tt&gt;property&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;value&lt;/tt&gt; parameters from&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
lctl nodemap_modify ... --property readonly_mount --value 1&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;to&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;lctl nodemap_modify ... --property readonly_mount=1&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
